nodes.text: The Sienar-Chall Utilipede Transport was a type of transport vessel. The chef Strono Tuggs owned a modified starship of this class, which he converted into a mobile kitchen and restaurant to take his traveling diner Tuggs' Grub to Docking Bay 7 Food and Cargo on Batuu.

The Sienar-Chall Utilipede Transport was created for Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge. It was first shown in a scale model for Galaxy's Edge during Disney's 2017 D23 Expo. Its name was identified in a reveal on February 27, 2019.
